Class AlertServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.base.AbstractComponentService<AlertComponentType,Alert>
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.alert.AlertServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
AlertService
public class AlertServiceImpl extends AbstractComponentService<AlertComponentType,Alert> implements AlertService
Default implementation of AlertService that manages retrieval and interactions with various Alert implementations.

This class leverages a cache for created alert components, reducing overhead when performing repeated operations. Each method delegates to a retrieved or newly created Alert instance appropriate to the given AlertComponentType.
